<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Staying In and Staying Well During COVID-19</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="3fc68533-2ca4-4881-99c5-e9e4cf93083a" >

    <p>We are experiencing a global health event and during this time, it is not uncommon for people to experience: anxiety, worry, fear and sadness; tearfulness and/or loss of interest in enjoyable activities; hopelessness, stress, or overwhelm; and difficulty concentrating and/or sleeping. These are challenging times but there are healthy ways to cope and manage our wellbeing.</p> 
<p>It is helpful to intentionally take moments to focus on what feels good, safe and stable.</p> 
<p>Seek medical advice if you are not feeling well and may be experiencing COVID-19 symptoms: call Telehealth Ontario for assistance 1-866-797-0000.</p>
    





</div>
