                        <a id="accordion-1584725908425-maintain-an-adapted-daily-routine" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#bfc0e323-bf60-448a-99c6-83eda6778558" href="#accordion-content-1584725908425-maintain-an-adapted-daily-routine" aria-controls="accordion-content-1584725908425-maintain-an-adapted-daily-routine" aria-expanded="false">
                            Maintain an adapted daily routine
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1584725908425-maintain-an-adapted-daily-routine" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1584725908425-maintain-an-adapted-daily-routine">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1584725908425 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="06acaeda-e48e-4a86-9a9b-4ca2f6448fa0" >

    <p>During these times, having a healthy routine will have a positive impact on your mood, thoughts, and feelings.</p> 
<p>Try…</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Sticking to regular mealtimes</li> 
 <li>Starting your day at the same time as normal</li> 
 <li>Structuring your day so you can stay on top of your academic requirements</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#06acaeda-e48e-4a86-9a9b-4ca2f6448fa0");});</script></div>

