                            Look after yourself
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1584725914207-look-after-yourself" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1584725914207-look-after-yourself">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1584725914207 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="b63dc943-eff5-4e8b-ad3d-8747045bcea1" >

    <p>Take things/tasks one step or day at a time to reduce overwhelm and increase a sense of control and capacity to cope in difficult times.</p> 
<p>Try…</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Eating healthy meals and snacks</li> 
 <li>Exercise regularly&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>Get plenty of sleep</li> 
 <li>Avoid alcohol and other drugs</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
