                            Stay connected while observing  social distancing
                        </a>
                    </h2>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1584725919642-stay-connected-while-observing--social-distancing" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1584725919642-stay-connected-while-observing--social-distancing">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1584725919642 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="6dfafb2c-5010-4d93-b05f-1406c95f68ee" >

    <p>Connecting with friends and family through phone calls, video chats or social media and sharing in this experience goes a long way to reduce feelings of isolation. When we talk about our thoughts and feelings, it helps us find ways to cope with stressful situations.</p> 
<p>Try…</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Maintaining your relationship with others using technology</li> 
 <li>Share your concerns about how you are feeling with a friend or family member</li> 
 <li>Setting up a regular group call with your friends</li> 
</ul>
    





